title: Windows 7 SP1 AIO 11in1 ESD pt-BR Sep 2016 {Gen2}
description:
* Windows 7 SP1 AIO 11in1 ESD pt-BR Sep 2016 {Gen2}


[ RELEASE INFO ]


* File: WIN7AIO.ESD.pt-BR.Sep2016.iso
* Size: 4,80GB
* Format: Bootable ISO

* Sources:  
* 32bit: dvd-677457 & 677686
* 64bit: dvd-677358 & 677668

* CRC32: 78612a33
* MD5: 22b4166bcce2e756539f01802d7c89eb
* SHA-1: d558a2fb211b4943f73ec594e78d958a53420b77

[ LANGUAGE ]

* pt-BR = BRAZILIAN 

[ CONTENTS ]

* Integrated / Pre-installed:

* Internet Explorer 11
* .NET Framework 4.6.2
* Windows Defender Updates
* Important & Security Updates - 2016-09-13

( Telemetry & Get Windows 10-updates are excluded )

* Setupcomplete / Post-install:

* DirectX End-User Runtimes (June 2010)
 
[ FEATURES ]

* install.wim compressed to recovery format (install.esd)
* Diagnostics and Recovery Toolset 10.0 (Microsoft DaRT)

[ EDITIONS INCLUDED ]

* 32bit:
* Windows 7 Starter
* Windows 7 Home Basic
* Windows 7 Home Premium
* Windows 7 Professional
* Windows 7 Enterprise
* Windows 7 Ultimate

* 64bit:
* Windows 7 Home Basic
* Windows 7 Home Premium
* Windows 7 Professional
* Windows 7 Enterprise
* Windows 7 Ultimate

* Activators: Daz Loader v2.2.2.0 & KMS
( Both Activators Potential False Positive Virus Alarm )

[ ACTIVATION INSTRUCTIONS ]

 * A WPI-window will pop up in the last phase of the installation.
 * To skip activation, just click on "Exit".   
 * To activate Enterprise, select "KMS". 
 * For all other editions, select "Windows Loader".
 * To execute your choise, click on "Begin Install".

( A video clip of how it works is attached )

[ SCREENSHOTS ]
[url]https://extraimago.com/image/wboW[/url]

[ INSTALLATION & INFORMATION ]

* NOTE! Only clean installs, no upgrades.
* Create bootable USB (highly recommended) with Rufus,
* (attached) or burn to DVD-DL at slow speed.

[ CREDITS ]

* ashish.k, milrob & stevie-boy 
* for continued support & help with user questions.

* Hope you will enjoy this release!

* Regards,
* Generation2 @ ET & TPB
